name: Survival of the fittest
description:
189 frame animation at 8fps. Red is hungry. Red is willing to risk the wrath of Momma Blue just to get some nom nom. Baby Blue is scared, and feels all alone, running for their lives. Red can smell the fear. So can Momma Blue as she catches up to Red. Pink is angry because Momma Blue is. And it's just another day in the rat race for Purple, Yellow, Green, and Orange. Enjoy!
